titles.title: A joint resolution approving the extension of nondiscriminatory treatment (most-favored-nation treatment) to the products of Romania.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S8525)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 7/1/1993--Introduced. Approves the extension of nondiscriminatory treatment (most-favored-nation treatment) to the products of Romania pursuant to the message transmitted to the Congress by the President on June 22, 1992.
